Sakur（撒固兒部落）

Itiniay i Hualien Cen no Hualien ko Sakur a niyaro’, 616  ko sa’osi no parod no loma’, 1,699 ko sa’osi no tamdaw.

39% ko ka’aloman no Yincomin, polong han i, 658  ko tamdaw; o roma sato i, 61% ko ka’aloman no roma a finacadan, polong han i, 1,041 ko tamdaw.

O pa-sin-to(百分比) no ka’aloman no tamdaw no kasafinacadan i, ko Amis25%, 撒奇拉雅族8%, Bunun1%, Tayal1%, Truku3%, roma1%.

Ira ko picodadan(興福國小、興福國小附幼) i niyaro’.

